3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with generative models and disentanglement of latent spaces, which are important topics in AI research. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with image generation and manipulation. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image generation and manipulation, which are important topics in multimedia research.
